examples.en: Light was pouring into the courtyard.
I could hear voices in the courtyard below my window.
She stood on a balcony looking down into the courtyard.
Several marble statues grace the courtyard.
We passed through the gates into a courtyard behind.
A small fountain splashed musically in the courtyard.
The play's opening scene takes place in the courtyard.
He ran across the courtyard, dodging a storm of bullets.
